- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new approach to improve the performance of recurrent neural networks, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The proposed model is a type of recurrent neural network, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper uses human activity datasets, which are often used in multimedia research, and the proposed model can potentially be applied to other types of sequential multimedia data.
